      "content": "i get what u saying but i really cant go. i looked online and people say most eye redness is just from digital eye strain or allergies. if i just use the drops and maybe take some antihistamines if the itching gets worse, would that be a safe way to manage it at home for a few days? i just need to know if i can handle this myself till the weekend.",
